{"about_the_game":"<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u2015Features\u2015</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique Puzzle Experience: Dive into an addictive and refreshing cube puzzle game!<br></li><li>Inventory Management: Strategically place items and build your unique setup!<br></li><li>Roguelite Elements: Experience new strategies and encounters with each run!</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/gameplaygif.gif?t=1718431886\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/puzzle.gif?t=1718431886\" /><br>The game features a 4\u00d74\u00d74 grid of mini-cubes. Swipe in any of the six directions, and all mini-cubes move accordingly. When three or more same-colored cubes align in the direction of movement, they merge and burst, triggering an attack! Combine multiple bursts at once for even greater damage.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/sii.png?t=1718431886\" /><br><br>Sometimes, small companions called 'Sii' are born from the mini-cubes. These loyal allies automatically attack enemies but have short lifespans. Use items to extend their lifespans and maximize their effectiveness.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/Inventory.gif?t=1718431886\" /><br>Strategically place items and 'Sii' to advance with your unique strategies.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u2015People Standing by 'Pathway'\u2015</h2></strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/character.png?t=1718431886\" /><br>On your journey, you may encounter the mysterious 'Pathway' Here, you will meet various characters. What is their connection to the 'CUBEN'...?<br><br>Get ready for an engaging puzzle adventure